0 WRO 2026 Senior — Barrier with ball on top (×4)
0 Per the rules-PDF page 6 photo: 4 barriers (2 red bodies with
0 blue balls + 2 black bodies with red balls) around the central
0 mosaic area. lego_prop's color="..." selects the BODY colour;
0 the ball is approximated as another brick (LDraw doesn't have
0 a clean "round 2x2 ball" part the WRO set uses; we use the
0 round 2x2 brick 30000 in 45811 if available, or fall back to
0 stacked 2x2 bricks).
